a:17:{s:4:"name";s:14:"Tretinoin 0,05";s:11:"small_descr";s:43:"Tretinoin Cream is used for treating acne. ";s:14:"small_descr_de";s:57:"Tretinoin Crème wird zur Behandlung von Akne verwendet. ";s:14:"small_descr_fr";s:52:"Tretinoin crème est utilisée pour traiter l'acné.";s:14:"small_descr_es";s:46:"Tretinoin Cream es usado para tratar el acné.";s:14:"small_descr_it";s:43:"Tretinoin Cream si usa per trattare l'acne.";s:10:"full_descr";s:5601:"<p><strong>INDICATIONS</strong></p><p>Tretinoin Cream is used for treating acne. Tretinoin Cream works in the skin to reduce the formation of acne and to help acne heal more quickly.</p><p><br /> <strong>INSTRUCTIONS </strong></p><p>Use Tretinoin Cream as directed by your doctor.</p><ul><li>Tretinoin Cream is for external use only.</li><li>Remove all cosmetics with a mild soap before applying Tretinoin Cream. Gently dry the area. Wait 20 to 30 minutes to make sure that skin is completely dry.</li><li>Squeeze a small amount (quarter inch or less) of the medicine onto the fingertip. This should be enough to cover the entire affected area. </li><li>Wash your hands immediately after using Tretinoin Cream.</li><li>If you miss a dose of Tretinoin Cream, skip the missed dose and go back to your regular dosing schedule. Do not use 2 doses at once.</li></ul><p>Ask your health care provider any questions you may have about how to use Tretinoin Cream.</p><p><strong>STORAGE</strong></p><p>Store Tretinoin Cream at room temperature, between 59 and 80 degrees F (15 and 26 degrees C). Store in a tightly closed container. Store away from heat and light. Keep Tretinoin Cream out of the reach of children and away from pets.<br /> <br /></p><p><strong>SAFETY INFORMATION</strong></p><p><strong>Do NOT use Tretinoin Cream if:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>you are allergic to any ingredient in Tretinoin Cream.</li>
</ul>
<p>Some medical conditions may interact with Tretinoin Cream. Tell your doctor or pharmacist if you have any medical conditions, especially if any of the following apply to you:</p>
<ul>
<li>if you are pregnant, planning to become pregnant, or are breast-feeding</li>
<li>if you are taking any prescription or nonprescription medicine, herbal preparation, or dietary supplement</li>
<li>if you have allergies to medicines, foods, or other substances</li>
<li>if you have eczema, an abnormally high white blood cell count, diabetes, or a sunburn.</li>
</ul>
<p>Some medicines may interact with Tretinoin Cream. Tell your health care provider if you are using any other medicines, especially any of the following:</p>
<ul>
<li>Topical medicines containing alcohol, resorcinol, sulfur, or salicylic acid because the risk of excessive skin dryness or irritation may occur.</li>
</ul>
<p>Ask your health care provider if Tretinoin Cream may interact with other medicines that you take. Check with your health care provider before you start, stop, or change the dose of any medicine</p>
<h3><strong>Important safety information:</strong></h3>
<ul>
<li>Tretinoin Cream is for external use only. Avoid getting Tretinoin Cream in your eyes, nose, or mouth. If you get Tretinoin Cream in your eyes, rinse thoroughly with water.</li>
<li>Tretinoin Cream may cause you to become sunburned more easily. Avoid the sun, sunlamps, or tanning booths until you know how you react to Tretinoin Cream. Use a sunscreen or wear protective clothing if you must be outside for more than a short time.</li>
<li>For the first 2 to 3 weeks of treatment, your skin condition may appear to worsen. This is expected. Do not stop using Tretinoin Cream at this time.</li>
<li>Talk with your doctor before you use any other medicines or products on your skin. While you are using Tretinoin Cream, you may use cosmetics.</li>
<li>Do not apply Tretinoin Cream to skin that is sunburned. Wait until the burn is fully healed before using Tretinoin Cream.</li>
<li>Do NOT use more than the recommended dose or use for longer than prescribed without checking with your doctor.</li>
<li>Avoid using other topical medication, cosmetics, or other products that have a strong drying effect. If you have dry skin from using these products, allow your skin to "rest" before using Tretinoin Cream.</li>
<li>Do not use Tretinoin Cream for any condition other than that for which it was prescribed.</li>
<li>Weather extremes, such as windy or cold weather, may irritate your skin more while you are using Tretinoin Cream.</li>
<li>Tretinoin Cream may cause harm if it is swallowed. If you may have taken it by mouth, contact your poison control center or emergency room right away.</li>
<li>Tretinoin Cream should be used with extreme caution in children younger 12 years; safety and effectiveness in these children have not been confirmed.</li>
<li>Pregnancy and breast-feeding: If you become pregnant, contact your doctor. You will need to discuss the benefits and risks of using Tretinoin Cream while you are pregnant. It is not known if Tretinoin Cream is found in breast milk after topical use. If you are or will be breast-feeding while you use Tretinoin Cream, check with your doctor. Discuss any possible risks to your baby.</li>
</ul><p><strong>SIDE EFFECTS</strong></p><p>All medicines may cause side effects, but many people have no, or minor, side effects.</p>
<p>Check with your doctor if any of these most common side effects persist or become bothersome:</p>
<p>Increase or decrease of skin pigment (color); redness, peeling, or feeling of warmth; sensitivity to sunlight; skin irritation; stinging at the application site.<br /> <br /> Seek medical attention right away if any of these severe side effects occur:</p>
<p>Severe allergic reactions (rash; hives; itching; difficulty breathing; tightness in the chest; swelling of the mouth, face, lips, or tongue); severe redness, swelling, blistering, or crusting of the skin.<br /> <br />&nbsp;This is not a complete list of all side effects that may occur. If you have questions about side effects, contact your health care provider.</p>";s:13:"full_descr_de";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_fr";s:15916:"<p><strong><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">INDICATIONS</span></span></strong></p><p><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">Tretinoin Cream est</span> <span class="hps">utilis&eacute; pour traiter</span> <span class="hps">l'acn&eacute;.</span> <span class="hps">Tretinoin Cream</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">fonctionne dans</span> <span class="hps">la peau pour r&eacute;duire</span> <span class="hps">la formation</span> <span class="hps">de l'acn&eacute; et</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">pour la</span> <span class="hps">gu&eacute;rir plus rapidement.</span></span></p><p><strong>A</strong><strong>DMINISTRATION</strong></p><p><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">Utilisez Tretinoin cr&egrave;me</span> <span class="hps">comme indiqu&eacute; par votre</span> <span class="hps">m&eacute;decin.</span></span></p><ul><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">Evitez l'ingestion</span> <span class="hps">de</span> <span class="hps">Tretinoin</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">Cream</span><span>.</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Retirez</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">tout les cosm&eacute;tiques avec</span> <span class="hps">un savon doux</span> <span class="hps">avant d'appliquer</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">Tretinoin cr&egrave;me</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">S&eacute;chez d&eacute;licatement</span> <span class="hps">la zone</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">Attendez de 20</span> <span class="hps">&agrave; 30 minutes pour</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">vous </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">assurer que</span> <span class="hps">la peau</span> <span class="hps">soit compl&egrave;tement s&egrave;che.</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">Pressez une petite quantit&eacute;</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">(le quart de pouce</span> <span class="hps">ou moins</span><span>) du m&eacute;dicament</span> <span class="hps">sur ​​le</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">bout du doigt</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">Cela devrait &ecirc;tre suffisant</span> <span class="hps">pour couvrir</span> <span class="hps">toute la zone touch&eacute;e</span><span>.</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Lavez les</span> <span class="hps">mains imm&eacute;diatement</span> <span class="hps">apr&egrave;s l'utilisation de</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">Tretinoin Cream</span><span>.</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Si vous</span> <span class="hps">manquez une dose de</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">Tretinoin Cream</span><span>, sautez la</span> <span class="hps">dose oubli&eacute;e et</span> <span class="hps">reprenez votre</span> <span class="hps">programme de dosage r&eacute;gulier</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">N'utilisez pas 2</span> <span class="hps">doses &agrave; la fois</span><span>.</span></span></li></ul><p>Si vous avez des questions sur l'utilisation de <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">Tretinoin Cream, </span></span>contactez votre m&eacute;decin<span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span>.</span></span></p><p><strong>CONSERVATION</strong></p><p>Gardez <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">Tretinoin Cream </span></span>&agrave;  la temp&eacute;rature ambiante, entre 59 et 80 degr&eacute;s F (15 et 26 degr&eacute;s C).  Entreposez loin de la chaleur et l'humidit&eacute; dans une bo&icirc;te ferm&eacute;e,   r&eacute;sistante &agrave; la lumi&egrave;re. Gardez <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">Tretinoin Cream </span></span>hors de la port&eacute;e des enfants et loin des animaux.</p><p><strong>RENSEIGNEMENTS DE SÉCURITÉ</strong></p><p><strong>N'utilisez pas </strong><strong>Tretinoin Cream si:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>vous &ecirc;tes allergique &agrave; un ingr&eacute;dient de Tretinoin Cream.</li>
</ul>
<p>Certaines  conditions m&eacute;dicales peuvent interagir avec Tretinoin Cream.   Informez votre  m&eacute;decin ou votre pharmacien si vous avez des conditions   m&eacute;dicales,  surtout si une des conditions suivantes s'applique &agrave; vous:</p>
<ul>
<li>si vous &ecirc;tes enceinte, envisagez de devenir enceinte, ou allaitez</li>
<li>si vous prenez une ordonnance ou un m&eacute;dicament en vente libre, une pr&eacute;paration d'herbes ou un suppl&eacute;ment alimentaire</li>
<li>si vous avez des allergies aux m&eacute;dicaments, aliments ou autres substances</li>
<li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">si</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">vous avez l'ecz&eacute;ma</span><span class="alt-edited">,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">la num&eacute;ration anormalement &eacute;lev&eacute;e des globules blancs</span><span class="alt-edited">, le diab&egrave;te ou</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">des coups de soleil</span><span>.</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p>Certains m&eacute;dicaments peuvent interagir avec Tretinoin Cream. Informez  votre   m&eacute;decin si vous prenez d'autres m&eacute;dicaments, en particulier les  &eacute;l&eacute;ments   suivants:</p>
<ul>
<li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">Les m&eacute;dicaments topiques</span> <span class="hps">contenant de l'alcool</span><span class="alt-edited">, r&eacute;sorcinol,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">acide</span> <span class="hps">sulfureux,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">ou acide salicylique</span><span>, car le risque</span> <span class="hps">de s&eacute;cheresse</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">excessive ou une irritation de la peau</span> <span class="hps">peut se produire</span><span>.</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p>Demandez &agrave; votre m&eacute;decin si Tretinoin Cream peut interagir avec   d'autres  m&eacute;dicaments que vous prenez. V&eacute;rifiez aupr&egrave;s de votre   pharmacien avant  de commencer, arr&ecirc;ter ou modifier la dose de tout   m&eacute;dicament.</p>
<p><strong>Information de s&eacute;curit&eacute; importante:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Tretinoin Cream</span> <span class="hps">est pour</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">l'utilisation externe seulement</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">&Eacute;vitez tout contact de</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">Tretinoin Cream</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">avec vos</span> <span class="hps">yeux, le nez</span> <span class="hps">ou la bouche.</span> <span class="hps">Si vous &ecirc;tes</span> <span class="hps">Tretinoin Cream</span> <span class="hps">dans vos yeux</span><span class="alt-edited">, baignez les yeux</span> <span class="hps">avec de l'eau</span><span>.</span></span></li>
<li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Tretinoin Cream</span> <span class="hps">peut</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">provoquer</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">des coups de soleil</span> <span class="hps">plus facilement.</span> <span class="hps">&Eacute;vitez le soleil,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">des lampes solaires, ou</span> <span class="hps">les cabines de bronzage</span> <span class="hps">avant de savoir comment</span> <span class="hps">vous r&eacute;agissez &agrave; Tretinoin</span> <span class="hps">Cream</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">Utilisez un &eacute;cran solaire</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">ou portez</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">des </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">v&ecirc;tements protecteurs si vous</span> <span class="hps">devez &ecirc;tre dehors pendant</span> <span class="hps">un certain temps.</span></span></li>
<li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">Pendant les 2</span> <span class="hps">&agrave; 3 premi&egrave;res</span> <span class="hps">semaines de traitement</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">votre &eacute;tat de peau</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">peut s'aggraver</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">Cela est pr&eacute;vu.</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">Ne</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">cessez pas d'utiliser</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">Tretinoin Cream</span> <span class="hps">pour le moment.</span></span></li>
<li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Discutez avec votre m&eacute;decin</span> <span class="hps atn">avant d'utiliser d'</span><span>autres m&eacute;dicaments ou produits</span> <span class="hps">sur votre peau.</span> <span class="hps">Pendant que vous</span> <span class="hps">utilisez Tretinoin Cream</span><span>, vous pouvez</span> <span class="hps">utiliser des produits cosm&eacute;tiques</span><span>.</span></span></li>
<li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">N'appliquez pas</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">Tretinoin Cream</span> <span class="hps">sur une peau</span> <span class="hps">qui est</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">br&ucirc;l&eacute;e par le soleil</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">Attendez jusqu'&agrave; ce que</span> <span class="hps">la br&ucirc;lure est</span> <span class="hps">totalement</span> <span class="hps">gu&eacute;ri avant d'utiliser</span> <span class="hps">Tretinoin Cream.</span></span></li>
<li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">N'utilisez pas</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">plus que la</span> <span class="hps">dose recommand&eacute;e</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">ou</span> <span class="hps">plus longtemps que prescrit</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">sans v&eacute;rification avec votre</span> <span class="hps">m&eacute;decin.</span></span></li>
<li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">&Eacute;vitez d'utiliser</span> <span class="hps">d'autres</span> <span class="hps">m&eacute;dicaments topiques</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">cosm&eacute;tiques</span> <span class="hps">ou</span> <span class="hps">autres produits</span> <span class="hps">qui ont un</span> <span class="hps">fort effet</span> <span class="hps">de s&eacute;chage.</span> <span class="hps">Si vous</span> <span class="hps">avez la peau s&egrave;che</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">apr&egrave;s l'utilisation de</span> <span class="hps">ces produits</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">permettez</span> <span class="hps">&agrave; votre peau de</span> <span class="hps atn">"</span><span class="alt-edited">reposer</span><span>" avant d'utiliser</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">Tretinoin Cream</span><span>.</span></span></li>
<li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">N'</span><span class="hps alt-edited">utilisez pas Tretinoin Cream</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">pour une autre condition</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">que</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">celle pour laquelle</span> <span class="hps">il a &eacute;t&eacute; prescrit.</span></span></li>
<li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Les conditions m&eacute;t&eacute;orologiques extr&ecirc;mes</span><span class="alt-edited">, tels que le</span> <span class="hps">temps venteux</span> <span class="hps">ou froid</span><span class="alt-edited">, peuvent irriter votre</span> <span class="hps">peau plus</span> <span class="hps">lorsque vous utilisez</span> <span class="hps">Tretinoin Cream.</span></span></li>
<li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Tretinoin Cream</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">peut &ecirc;tre dangereux</span> <span class="hps">s'il est aval&eacute;</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">Si</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">vous l'avez</span> <span class="hps">pris par </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">la bouche</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">contactez votre centre</span> <span class="hps">antipoison ou la salle</span> <span class="hps">d'urgence imm&eacute;diatement.</span></span></li>
<li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Tretinoin Cream</span> <span class="hps">devrait &ecirc;tre utilis&eacute;</span> <span class="hps">avec une extr&ecirc;me prudence</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">aux </span> <span class="hps alt-edited">enfants au-dessous de 12 ans</span><span>, la s&eacute;curit&eacute;</span> <span class="hps">et l'efficacit&eacute;</span> <span class="hps">de ces enfants n'ont</span> <span class="hps">pas &eacute;t&eacute; confirm&eacute;es.</span></span></li>
<li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">La grossesse</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">et l'allaitement</span><span>:</span> <span class="hps">Si vous tombez enceinte</span><span>, contactez votre m&eacute;decin</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">Vous</span> <span class="hps">aurez besoin de discuter</span> <span class="hps">les</span> <span class="hps">avantages et les risques</span> <span class="hps">de l'utilisation de </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Tretinoin Cream</span> <span class="hps">pendant que vous</span> <span class="hps">&ecirc;tes enceinte</span><span>. </span></span><br /><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">On n'est pas connu</span> <span class="hps">si</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">Tretinoin Cream</span> <span class="hps">passe dans le lait</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">maternel apr&egrave;s l'application topique</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">Si vous &ecirc;tes ou </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">serez</span> <span class="hps">d'allaiter pendant que</span> <span class="hps">vous utilisez</span> <span class="hps">Tretinoin Cream</span><span>, v&eacute;rifiez aupr&egrave;s de</span> <span class="hps">votre m&eacute;decin</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">Discutez de tout risque</span> <span class="hps">&eacute;ventuel pour votre b&eacute;b&eacute;</span><span>.</span></span></li>
</ul><p><strong>LES EFFETS SECONDAIRES</strong></p><p>Tout les m&eacute;dicaments peuvent causer des effets secondaires, mais    beaucoup de gens n'ont pas, ou ont des effets secondaires mineurs.</p>
<p>Consultez votre m&eacute;decin si l'un de ces effets ind&eacute;sirables persiste ou devient g&ecirc;nant:</p>
<p><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">L'augmentation ou la diminution de</span> <span class="hps">pigmentation de la peau</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">(la couleur</span><span class="alt-edited">), la rougeur</span><span class="alt-edited">, la exfoliation ou</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">la sensation de chaleur</span><span class="alt-edited">, la sensibilit&eacute; &agrave; la</span> <span class="hps">lumi&egrave;re du soleil,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">l'irritation de la peau</span><span>;</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">le picotement</span> <span class="hps">au site d'application</span><span>.</span></span></p>
<p>Consultez un m&eacute;decin imm&eacute;diatement si l'un de ces effets ind&eacute;sirables s&eacute;v&egrave;res se produit:</p>
<p>Les r&eacute;actions allergiques graves (l'&eacute;ruption cutan&eacute;e, l'urticaire, la    d&eacute;mangeaison, la difficult&eacute; &agrave; respirer, la sensation d'oppression dans    la poitrine, l'enflure de la bouche, du visage, des l&egrave;vres ou de la    langue), <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">la rougeur grave</span><span class="alt-edited">, le gonflement, la v&eacute;sication</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">les cro&ucirc;tes</span> <span class="hps">de la peau</span><span>.</span></span></p>
<p>Ce n'est pas une liste compl&egrave;te de tout les effets secondaires qui    peuvent survenir. Si vous avez des questions sur des effets secondaires,    veuillez communiquer avec votre m&eacute;decin.</p>";s:13:"full_descr_es";s:6708:"<p><strong>INDICACIONES</strong></p><p>Tretinoin Cream es utilizado para el tratamiento del acn&eacute;. Tretinoin Cream funciona en la piel para reducir la formaci&oacute;n de acn&eacute; y para curar acn&eacute; m&aacute;s r&aacute;pidamente.</p><p><strong>INSTRUCCIONES</strong></p><p>Utilice Tretinoin Cream como es indicado por el m&eacute;dico.</p><ul><li>Tretinoin Cream es solamente para el uso externo.</li><li>Elimine todos los cosm&eacute;ticos con un jab&oacute;n suave antes de aplicar Tretinoin Cream. Seque suavemente el &aacute;rea. Espere de 20 a 30 minutos para  asegurarse de que la piel es completamente seca.</li><li>Estruje una peque&ntilde;a cantidad (un cuarto de pulgada o menos) de la medicina sobre el dedo &iacute;ndice. Esto debe ser suficiente para cubrir toda el &aacute;rea afectada.</li><li>L&aacute;ve las manos inmediatamente despu&eacute;s de usar Tretinoin Cream.</li><li>Si olvida una dosis de Tretinoin Cream, omita la dosis olvidada y vuelva a su horario regular de dosificaci&oacute;n. No use 2 dosis al mismo tiempo.</li></ul><p>Consulte con su m&eacute;dico si tiene cualquiera pregunta sobre utilizaci&oacute;n de Tretinoin Cream.</p><p><strong>ALMACENAMIENTO</strong></p><p>Almacene Tretinoin Cream a temperatura ambiente, entre 59 y 80 grados F (15 y  26 grados C). Almacene en un envase herm&eacute;ticamente cerrado.&nbsp; Almacene  lejos del calor y de la luz. Almacene Tretinoin Cream fuera del alcance de  ni&ntilde;os y animales dom&eacute;sticos.</p><p><strong>INFORMACIÓN DE SEGURIDAD</strong></p><p><strong>NO use Tretinoin Cream si:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Usted es al&eacute;rgico a cualquier ingrediente de Tretinoin Cream.</li>
</ul>
<p>Algunas condiciones m&eacute;dicas pueden interactuar con Tretinoin Cream. D&iacute;ga a  su m&eacute;dico o farmac&eacute;utico si tiene alguna condici&oacute;n m&eacute;dica, especialmente  alguno de los casos siguientes:</p>
<ul>
<li>si est&aacute; embarazada, planea caer embarazada o si amamanta</li>
<li>si Usted toma cualquiera prescripci&oacute;n o medicamento sin receta, la preparaci&oacute;n a base de hierbas o suplemento diet&eacute;tico</li>
<li>si Usted tiene alergias a medicamentos, alimentos o otras sustancias</li>
<li>si Usted tiene eczema, un nivel de gl&oacute;bulos blancos anormalmente alto, o una quemadura de sol.</li>
</ul>
<p>Algunos medicamentos pueden interactuar con Tretinoin Cream. Diga a su m&eacute;dico si Usted usa otros medicamentos, especialmente cualquier de los siguientes:</p>
<ul>
<li>Los medicamentos t&oacute;picos que contienen alcohol, resorcinol, &aacute;cido de azufre, o &aacute;cido salic&iacute;lico, porque el riesgo de sequedad excesiva de la piel o irritaci&oacute;n puede ocurrir.</li>
</ul>
<p>Pregunte a su m&eacute;dico si Tretinoin Cream puede interactuar con otros  medicamentos que toma. Consulte con su m&eacute;dico antes de iniciar, detener o  cambiar la dosis de un medicamento.</p>
<p><strong>Informaci&oacute;n importante sobre seguridad:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Tretinoin Cream es solamente para uso externo. Evite el impacto deTretinoin Cream en los ojos, la nariz o la boca. Si Tretinoin Cream da en los ojos, enjuague con agua.</li>
<li>Tretinoin Cream puede causar que se quema con m&aacute;s facilidad. Evite el sol, las l&aacute;mparas solares o las cabinas de bronceado hasta que sepa cu&aacute;l es su reacci&oacute;n a Tretinoin Cream. Use un bloqueador solar o ropa protectora si debe estar fuera durante largo tiempo.</li>
<li>Durante las primeras 2 a 3 semanas de tratamiento, su condici&oacute;n de la piel puede parecer a empeorar. Es normal. No deje de usar Tretinoin Cream en este momento.</li>
<li>Consulte con su m&eacute;dico antes de usar cualquier otra medicina o productos en su piel. Mientras que usted est&aacute; utilizando Tretinoin Cream, puede usar los cosm&eacute;ticos.</li>
<li>No aplique Tretinoin Cream a la piel quemada por el sol. Espere hasta que la quemadura est&aacute; completamente curada antes de usar Tretinoin Cream.</li>
<li>No use m&aacute;s de la dosis recomendada o use por m&aacute;s tiempo que lo prescrito sin antes consultar con el m&eacute;dico.</li>
<li>Evite el uso de otros medicamentos t&oacute;picos, cosm&eacute;ticos o otros productos que tienen un fuerte efecto secante. Si tienes la piel seca por empleo de estos productos, permita que su piel "descansa" antes de usar Tretinoin Cream.</li>
<li>No utilice Tretinoin Cream para alguna condici&oacute;n para la que esto medicamento no fue recetado.</li>
<li>Los fen&oacute;menos meteorol&oacute;gicos extremos, tales como el clima ventoso o fr&iacute;o, pueden irritar su piel m&aacute;s mientras usa Tretinoin Cream.</li>
<li>Tretinoin Cream puede causar da&ntilde;o si es tragado. Si ha tomado por v&iacute;a oral, contacte con el centro de control de envenenamiento o la sala de emergencias inmediatamente.</li>
<li>Tretinoin Cream debe ser utilizado con precauci&oacute;n extrema en ni&ntilde;os menores de 12 a&ntilde;os; seguridad y eficacia en estos ni&ntilde;os no han sido confirmadas.</li>
<li>Embarazo y lactancia: Si se queda embarazada, consulte con el m&eacute;dico. Usted tendr&aacute; que discutir los beneficios y riesgos del uso de Tretinoin Cream durante el embarazo. No es conocido si Tretino&iacute;na crema se encuentra en la leche materna despu&eacute;s del uso t&oacute;pico. Si Usted amamanta o amamantar&aacute; mientras el empleo de Tretinoin Cream, consulte con su m&eacute;dico. Discuta cualquier riesgo posible para su beb&eacute;.</li>
</ul><p><strong>EFECTOS SECUNDARIOS</strong></p><p>Todos los medicamentos pueden causar efectos secundarios, pero muchas  personas no tienen, o tienen efectos secundarios menores. Consulte con  su m&eacute;dico si cualquier de estos efectos secundarios m&aacute;s comunes persiste  o se vuelve molesto:</p>
<p>Ampliaci&oacute;n o disminuci&oacute;n de pigmento de la piel (color), enrojecimiento, descamaci&oacute;n o sensaci&oacute;n de calor, sensibilidad a la luz solar, irritaci&oacute;n de la piel, picaz&oacute;n en el sitio de aplicaci&oacute;n.<br /><br />Busque atenci&oacute;n m&eacute;dica inmediatamente si alguno de estos efectos secundarios graves se produce:<br /><br />Las reacciones al&eacute;rgicas graves (erupci&oacute;n cut&aacute;nea, urticaria, picaz&oacute;n, dificultad para respirar, opresi&oacute;n en el pecho, hinchaz&oacute;n de la boca, cara, labios o lengua), enrojecimiento grave, hinchaz&oacute;n, ampollas o costras en la piel.</p>
